{"tid":1386721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"你班撚樣香港人醒下啦","createTime":"2019-07-30T11:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T03:20:30.000Z","uid":73267,"like":67,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"045122053b918b804ba5799bc2ad4108e3595873","tid":1386721,"uid":73267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:44:24.000Z","msg":"你班溫室小花唔好再得把口<br />\n比人踩到上心口都要繼續縮<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">對前線最大支持<br />\n唔係要你啲飯 唔係要你啲錢<br />\n係要你班撚樣一齊有玉石俱焚嘅精神<br />\n企係我地班前線隔離齊上齊落啊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n醒下啦！！！<br />\n呢個政府無撚得救架啦<br />\n睇到佢又話我地暴動<br />\n係咪好撚嬲 谷撚住道氣啊<br />\n係啊 個撚個都係咁啊 咁點啊！！？？<br />\n<br />\n垃圾政府繼續有佢講 你地繼續有你地淆<br />\n就係因為佢睇死你地惡唔出咩樣先咁肆無忌彈啊<br />\n醒下啦！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">佢話我地暴動 <br />\n我地就比佢知道咩叫真正嘅暴動</span></span><br />\n革命抗爭係會流血係會死人啊<br />\n遲下變做下等公民同死左有咩分別啊<br />\n對住暴政係無道理可講架<br />\n求大家睇清楚呢個世界啦<br />\n唔好再做溫室裡嘅小花啦<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港就黎玩撚完啦！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"5f3284ee164659c75dfe2f499da6e6b3d88d42c0","tid":1386721,"uid":23587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:45:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffb5c4eef996620eb303fbd65f35a6d8c71a698","tid":1386721,"uid":8948,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:45:35.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>玉石俱焚！六條人命，二百個年輕人既將來係晒我地手上！光復香港！時代革命！不撤不散！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"04cd119dd756d641b803670d144cc37aab887248","tid":1386721,"uid":73267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:47:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">前線要嘅唔係你地啲裝備唔係你地啲飯<br />\n係要你地係精神同信念層面上嘅改變啊！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"b431872be456ffeb890d7cdc6415b2dec1c8c750","tid":1386721,"uid":73267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:49:13.000Z","msg":"推比全部和理非睇<br />\n<br />\n前線要嘅支持唔係物質上<br />\n係精神同信念層面啊"},{"pid":"2b9e9cb0e0f889135cfd79e8c2686d2475e326a7","tid":1386721,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:49:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa8e2063b1f83411b7b747731d7ae7e3f86e7819","tid":1386721,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:50:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ccf19aa9aea106e572c3e3386a5028b1d077faf4","tid":1386721,"uid":73267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"746a6cd8a3bd4cc3a4d0eacd626f0343f97e0f05","tid":1386721,"uid":259329,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:50:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1182ce0e2d717f3bb3b9f47dafa389d762d3c131","tid":1386721,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:50:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bb4a79f7421035003dacf511653bbdf99cdf0da3","tid":1386721,"uid":73267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:51:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"753717b20d7d3f283e3fbe1a5fdb10cfb53dd755","tid":1386721,"uid":73267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:52:16.000Z","msg":"醒下啊！！！"},{"pid":"56b22efabbe374642907693c7abe39bfa80c6ea8","tid":1386721,"uid":73267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:53:36.000Z","msg":"比人爆頭都未撚驚<br />\n你地驚乜撚嘢啊"},{"pid":"553bad617c5d66dd62973ef560c22fc95fa4c8e6","tid":1386721,"uid":73267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T11:55:17.000Z","msg":"推啊"},{"pid":"5b7ac2d3b3e53fdec45f0b8ca2da685b6d2e7d75","tid":1386721,"uid":73267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"04cd119dd756d641b803670d144cc37aab887248","tid":1386721,"uid":73267,"like":1,"dislike":0,"sco